<br>
&quot;How's my driving?  Call (xxx) xxx-xxxx, the Judge wants to know.&quot;<br>
<br>
It's a trend that lately the judges are passing these kinds of sentences for minor infractions.  I'm all for it, but wanted to toss it up here for discussion.  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.worldfreeinternet.net/news/nws106.htm">Here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> is an article from the Worldfreeinternet that goes into it a bit.  Interesting stuff. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:medium;">Dante Moradis</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
