<br>
Road rage aside, I think it can do some good though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shehbahn>shehbahn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>No blood for oil!</span><br>  Posts: 1248<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/23/03 1:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=896.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: &quot;Shame Sentencing&quot;</span><hr size=1> &gt;It's a trend that lately the judges are passing these kinds of sentences for minor infractions.<br>
